    "body": "As mentioned in #11885, there's always a 2-tick Turn activity  running as ChildActivity in Move after an L-turn (occasionally in other situations, too), which is the culprit behind this (the actor is indeed not moving forward during that time-frame). Closing as duplicate of #11885."
